headline: GTA Online
subtitle: IN THE CLUB
content:
Hot Tip for Night Club Owners: Keep an eye out for texts from Marcel while you’re in the building. Things are always getting messy at the hottest club in town, but that means there are always chances to make some cash on the side.

Want to increase your returns even more? Additional Club Management missions are now available from the nightclub computer or by calling Tony Prince. Looking to source goods? Call Yohan and he’ll hook you up.
